, \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That propelled him into a contest with Sweden's Per Olofsson.\", \"from\": 802, \"to\": 863, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like his first repechage bout, Bey was not significantly pushed and cruised to a 7-1 victory.\", \"from\": 864, \"to\": 957, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 895, \"end\": 898, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.9999997916388783, \"rank\": 1.5813368908487221e-07, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Next up was Georgia's Iuri Lomadze in the bronze medal match.\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 1020, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 971, \"end\": 978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\", \"score\": 0.4919417179872382, \"rank\": 0.6647627269060259, \"text\": \"Georgia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgia_Bulldogs_football\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lomadze was a two-time European medalist, who earned a bronze in the continental tournament earlier this year.\", \"from\": 1021, \"to\": 1131, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lomadze appeared to have an early advantage as Bey was hit with passivity giving the Georgian wrestler an opportunity to work from par terre.\", \"from\": 1133, \"to\": 1274, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.9999997916388783, \"rank\": 1.5813368908487221e-07, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}, {\"begin\": 1218, \"end\": 1226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgians\", \"score\": 0.9786523973996306, \"rank\": 0.021614006559586316, \"text\": \"Georgian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though Lomadze was the top wrestler, it was Bey who countered for a four-point score of his own.\", \"from\": 1275, \"to\": 1371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1319, \"end\": 1322, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.9999997916388783, \"rank\": 1.5813368908487221e-07, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lomadze's corner challenged to no avail, which gave Bey a 5-1 lead.\", \"from\": 1372, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1424, \"end\": 1427, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.9999997916388783, \"rank\": 1.5813368908487221e-07, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Late in the second period, Lomadze hit a duck-under and put the American on his back, but it was deemed a two-point hold; not four points.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1578, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1504, \"end\": 1512, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999865247401222, \"rank\": 7.928785255837654e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bey avoided giving up a fall and escaped with a 5-4 victory.\", \"from\": 1579, \"to\": 1639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1579, \"end\": 1582, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.9999997916388783, \"rank\": 1.5813368908487221e-07, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the Olympics looming in the balance, the two bronze medalists, Bey and Hungary's Zoltan Levai squared off.\", \"from\": 1641, \"to\": 1752, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1712, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.9999997916388783, \"rank\": 1.5813368908487221e-07, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}, {\"begin\": 1717, \"end\": 1724, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"score\": 0.9807467457366411, \"rank\": 0.01963121890390552, \"text\": \"Hungary\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hungary\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"An unremarkable first period ended 2-0 in favor of Levai with the scoring coming from a passivity call and Bey stepping out while avoiding a throw attempt on the ensuing par terre restart.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1941, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1860, \"end\": 1863, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.9999997916388783, \"rank\": 1.5813368908487221e-07, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The second period started with Levai pushing the pace and controlling the center and therefore getting a second passivity point.\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 2071, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Bey wasn't able to really get to any favorable offensive positions until the final :20 seconds of the bout when he was shooting low up into the body.\", \"from\": 2073, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2073, \"end\": 2076, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.9999997916388783, \"rank\": 1.5813368908487221e-07, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those attempts were fended off by Levai and the clock hit zero on the match and Bey's hopes for Paris with a 3-0 loss.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2341, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2303, \"end\": 2306, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"score\": 0.9999997916388783, \"rank\": 1.5813368908487221e-07, \"text\": \"Bey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bey\"}, {\"begin\": 2319, \"end\": 2324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.999999994326572, \"rank\": 5.67338399139568e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Although women's freestyle took place on Friday, no American women were in action because all six weights had already been qualified for the Olympics.\", \"from\": 2343, \"to\": 2493, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2395, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9999865247401222, \"rank\": 7.928785255837654e-06, \"text\": \"American\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There are no comments to display.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2528, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You need to be a member in order to leave a comment  Sign up for a new account in our community.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2626, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's easy!\", \"from\": 2627, \"to\": 2637, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Already have an account?\", \"from\": 2639, \"to\": 2663, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sign in here.\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2677, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Show all categories  Copyright \\u00a9 2025 InterMatPowered by Invision Community\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2754, \"entities\": []}]}"